reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 3, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This packing cube set is disappointing. There is no difference in buying individual packing cubes from a dollar store (like Daiso) and these. I was disappointed in the compression components being just two flimsy straps built into the larger cubes. Real compression cubes have double zippers to compress the clothes down. The fabric is thin and feels cheap. I would not buy this again.
